# =========================================================================
# scalpel .gitignore
# =========================================================================
# This file controls what gets pushed to the public GitHub mirror. The
# guiding principle: ship the library, the tests, the CI, the TOMS
# manuscript bundle, and the reproducibility scripts. Everything else
# (session state, secrets, third-party PDFs, prior-draft directories,
# build artifacts) is excluded.

# --- Python build artifacts ----------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
spectral_scalpel.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/
*.so
*.ipynb_checkpoints/
.venv/
venv/
env/
.tox/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# --- LaTeX build artifacts -----------------------------------------------
*.aux
*.log
*.bbl
*.blg
*.synctex.gz
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.out
*.thm
*.toc
*.lof
*.lot
*.nav
*.snm
*.vrb
*.idx
*.ilg
*.ind
*.run.xml
*.bcf
*.cut

# --- Session state / IDE / secrets (NEVER push) --------------------------
.claude/
.cursor/
.aider*
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
secrets*
credentials*
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Repo-local development output (NOT for the public GitHub mirror) ----
# Per project scoping: the public GitHub repo contains the library
# (scalpel/, tests/, CI, root metadata) PLUS the self-contained
# reproducibility/ tree that CodeOcean and the RCR re-execution path
# consume. The manuscript prose (paper_toms/) and development reports
# (reports/) stay local; the Zenodo deposit mirrors GitHub. TOMS
# reviewers get the manuscript via the journal portal.
reports/
paper_toms/
scripts/*.png
scripts/*.pdf
# Reproducibility regenerated outputs (figures + diff_report) stay
# local; only the archived inputs in reproducibility/data/ are tracked.
reproducibility/figures/
reproducibility/data/diff_report.txt

# --- Third-party copyrighted PDFs (not ours to redistribute) -------------
1-s2.0-S0009250926004884-main.pdf
**/literature/

# --- Prior-draft / parallel-paper directories (NOT part of this submission) ----
# Each of these was an earlier or parallel manuscript; the public TOMS
# release ships only paper_toms/ as the manuscript bundle. The other
# directories remain in the private working copy.
paper/
paper2/
paper2_sisc/
paper_pnas/
paper_sisc/
paper_sisc_v2/
paper_v1_preNCSrevision/
nonlinear/
notebooks/
science_submission.tex
nl_nilt_paper.tex

# --- Template repos (vendored, not our code) -----------------------------
PNAS_template/
acmart-primary/

# --- Zenodo staging (large zip, not for git) ----------------------------
paper_toms/zenodo_v2_staging/scalpel-toms-v2.zip
paper_toms/zenodo_v2_staging/code.zip

# --- Misc local artifacts ------------------------------------------------
texput.log
*.local
